Jessica Hische
--------------

![jessicahische_press](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/8985471/5074413/007fbe2c-6e82-11e4-8ac8-3844cf3ff6a1.jpg)


Jessica is s an American letterer, illustrator, and type designer.

Jessica's work is very colourful and stands out from the crowd. I love how expressive her work comes across and how much each image gives off a story.

Jessica has a remarkably prolific career; she is known for her gorgeously elaborate custom lettering and illustration






Her work:
==========


