Paula Scher
-----------

Paula an American graphic designer, painter and art educator in design, and the first female principal at Pentagram, which she joined in 1991

Scher has developed identity and branding systems, promotional materials, environmental graphics, packaging, and publication designs for a broad range of clients that include, among others, Bloomberg, Coca-Cola, Perry Ellis, The Museum of Modern Art, Jazz at Lincoln Center






