Wolfgang Weingart
------------------
wolfgang weingart, who was born in 1941 in salemertal in southern germany, attended the merz akademie in stuttgart from 1958 to 1960, where he familiarised himself with typesetting and the process of making linocuts and woodcuts. after this he trained as a typesetter and discovered swiss typography.

His work
=========

![wolfgang weingart2-2](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/8985471/5086807/86803db2-6f18-11e4-861b-f5fa53746fbe.png)

